    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s looking for a new home! It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in great shape\u2014perfect for your daily commutes or those fun weekend adventures. It's been well-loved, runs like a champ, and is ready to hit the road with its next owner. Come take it for a spin, you're gonna love how it handles! Send me a message if you're interested!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS for optimal volumetric efficiency across the rev range. This example utilizes the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, delivering torque to the rear wheels via a limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with a reinforced subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and lateral stability this platform is known for. The exterior and interior reflect honest, well-cared-for mileage, making this an ideal specimen for the purist who demands mechanical integrity and a visceral driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs smooth. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents the perfect balance of performance and practicality. The exterior finish retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor, honest character marks consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, while every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended. As a non-smoker\u2019s car, the interior smells fresh and clean. Mechanically, this car stands out with a comprehensive service history. It has recently undergone a full multi-point inspection, including a fresh oil change and fluid top-off. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension provides a quiet, composed ride that feels tight on the road. Tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide confident stopping power. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to drive home with complete confidence.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, offering an ideal balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has been thoroughly vetted to ensure mechanical excellence and remains in commendable condition both inside and out. It represents a premier opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-caliber automobile without the premium of a showroom-new price point. Rigorously inspected and ready for immediate delivery.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for all your weekend adventures? I\u2019m parting with this beauty, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been really well-cared for over the years. It's the perfect match for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great on the road. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain chassis rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings, ensuring the communicative steering rack delivers the tactile feedback this platform is renowned for. Mechanically sound and aesthetically preserved, it represents a well-maintained specimen of BMW\u2019s peak naturally aspirated era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
